---
---
<section class="guarantee-section">
  <div class="guarantee-inner">
    <div class="grid">
      <div>
        <span class="section-label-dark">05 — Unsere Zusage</span>
        <h2 class="title">Prozess-Garantie statt Marketing-Versprechen.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="cards">
        <div class="gcard">
          <div class="gcard-num">GARANTIE 01</div>
          <p class="gcard-text">Transparente Fix-Offerte - keine versteckten Zusatzkosten ohne Ihre vorherige Freigabe.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="gcard">
          <div class="gcard-num">GARANTIE 02</div>
          <p class="gcard-text">Offerte innerhalb von 7 Tagen. Wenn nicht, ist die Beratung für Sie kostenlos.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .guarantee-section {
    padding: 96px 48px;
    background: var(--ink); color: #fff;
  }
  .guarantee-inner { max-width: 1440px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr;
    gap: 64px; align-items: center;
  }

  .title {
    font-size: 44px; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em; line-height: 1.05;
    margin: 0; color: #fff;
  }

  .cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; }

  .gcard {
    padding: 28px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }
  .gcard-num {
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px;
    opacity: 0.5; margin-bottom: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }
  .gcard-text {
    font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.55;
    margin: 0; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .guarantee-section { padding: 72px 20px; }
    .title { font-size: 32px; }
    .cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
